abstract: >
  Zero-dependency CLI that generates an LLM-optimized textual context from a codebase
  by emitting a deterministic ASCII directory tree followed by concatenated file
  contents. The tool applies safe-by-default heuristics for noise filtering,
  truncation of log-like files, and protection against stdout self-inclusion when
  redirecting output to a file within the scanned root.
